doctype html
html
  head
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    title About Us
    link(rel='stylesheet' href='/bootstrap/css/amelia.bootstrap.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/style.css')

  body
    nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.bg-dark.fixed-top
      a.navbar-brand(href='/') My Blog
      button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navbarSupportedContent', aria-controls='navbarSupportedContent', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
        span.navbar-toggler-icon
      #navbarSupportedContent.collapse.navbar-collapse
        ul.navbar-nav.mr-auto
          li.nav-item
            a.nav-link(href='/') Home
          li.nav-item
            a.nav-link(href='/about') About
          li.nav-item
            a.nav-link(href='/contact') Contact
        ul.navbar-nav.ml-auto
          li.nav-item
            a.nav-link(href='/login') Login 

    section.py-5
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-8.mx-auto
            h2.text-center.text-uppercase.mb-4 Our Story
            p.lead.text-muted.text-center
              | Welcome to our blog! We are passionate about sharing stories, ideas, and experiences with our readers. Our goal is to provide valuable insights, tips, and entertainment through our articles. Whether you're a seasoned reader or just discovering us, we hope you find our content engaging and inspiring.

            h2.text-center.text-uppercase.mt-5.mb-4 Our Mission
            p.lead.text-muted.text-center
              | Our mission is to create a space where people can connect, learn, and explore diverse topics. We believe in the power of words to spark conversations, encourage growth, and bring positive change. Through our blog, we aim to foster a community of curious minds and passionate readers.

            h2.text-center.text-uppercase.mt-5.mb-4 Meet the Team
            .row.justify-content-center
              .col-md-4
                .team-member.text-center
                  h4.mt-3
                    | Lokesh Chandra
                  p.text-muted
                    | Founder & Writer
    script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js')
    script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js')
    script(src='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js')